{"tid":958901,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"【咁玩嘢？】麥哥利高堅將改名為 「麥哥利麥哥利高堅高堅」","createTime":"2018-12-28T07:44:02.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-28T15:55:10.000Z","uid":130626,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"c1f47c50713c13881217e2e5ee66148ba112c81d","tid":958901,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-28T07:44:02.000Z","msg":"《寶貝智多星》（Home Alone）男星麥哥利高堅（Macaulay Culkin）曾因醜聞纏身而星途急轉直下，最近佢因為拍廣告重現《寶貝智多星》經典場面，而翻身成功人氣稍升，不過佢就宣佈將會改個騎呢名，名為「麥哥利麥哥利高堅高堅」（Macaulay Macaulay Culkin Culkin）！<br />\n事源係上個月佢於社交網話自己嘅中間名（middle name）好悶，仲叫大家投票幫佢揀個中間名，結果就由「麥哥利高堅」勝出，獲超過6萬票！所以夾埋佢本身個名，就成為「麥哥利麥哥利高堅高堅」！<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/iVjhhhm.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FiVjhhhm.png&h=e5d00545&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bSR3Xhm.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbSR3Xhm.png&h=968e1519&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/h8L4GJ2.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fh8L4GJ2.png&h=97351034&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"23dce0e72b123a33fe3c74194e04fce7c0de816c","tid":958901,"uid":46385,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-28T07:58:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ab4da6f0b776c373273f55c9c2d4399b29ffc49b","tid":958901,"uid":1914,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-28T08:05:49.000Z","msg":"諗起mike &quot;mike ross&quot; ross"},{"pid":"c75dfaa7e3f55864a11b6dda1001a7a06ddc436e","tid":958901,"uid":818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-28T08:06:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"533c6c65c8d45f09ccb9b163c7c222bd902404a9","tid":958901,"uid":82301,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0